message: Rename source/ to src/ and source-docs/ to src-docs
Update package.json, point main to dist/keen-ui.js
Remove build-min script, add copy-docs-html script
Update build scripts, add lib folder to 'files'
Remove horsey, add fuzzysearch for autocomplete
Move imports-loader to devDependencies, install merge-options (used in UiSelect)
Rename LICENSE to LICENCE in files array
Remove dominus in favor of classlist helper and native DOM methods

Major restructure for v1.0 development

- Use gulp and custom scripts for build system
- Temporarily remove test/ and test tools
- Update dependencies, Vue to 2.0
- Use Pug templating engine for static doc pages
- Adjust overall page styling and sidebar content

Rewrite all components to support Vue 2 and have a more consistent API

- Use BEM for CSS selector naming
- Remove UiRating and related components
- Remove draggabilly dependency
- Remove validatorjs dependency (validations should now be handled externally)
- Use Gulp for building
- Add new component: UiCheckboxGroup
Update build dependencies, update package meta data

Remove module field

As it causes Webpack to use the source by default
Adjust files field, add test script

Remove prism.js

Currently un-needed as there's only one place where it's applied.

Also rename routes.js to navigation.js since it contains the menu also.
Build docs when running build:all script

Refactor global prop config system, rewrite Customization guide

- Remove deprecated deep-assign for deepmerge
- Update CHANGELOG
Bind to 0.0.0.0 for external access, disable browser open for dev
Add production build script, bump version in build
Upgrade UiPopover and UiTooltip to Tippy.js 4

Bump node-sass from 4.9.2 to 4.13.1 (#507)

Bumps [node-sass](https://github.com/sass/node-sass) from 4.9.2 to 4.13.1.
